Z","msg":"年轉人<br />\n<br />\n好似 x men d friend 咁"},{"pid":"42e4c4449394d338d774dbc10a134ae946195d62","tid":149693,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"人工年年都會加<br />\n<br />\n但永遠都追唔上通脹<br />\n<br />\n日日打住無前途既工虛耗生命<br />\n<br />\n去到三十頭<br />\n<br />\n發覺你自己唔再後生<br />\n<br />\n但仲天真以為年年有人工加<br />\n<br />\n但你老細已經炒鳩左你<br />\n<br />\n用平d人工請左個後生取代你"},{"pid":"f06241cfba23a562006594eca72f744b7b9e417a","tid":149693,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"如果行頭細 技術性高  三十 打後已冇可能轉行"},{"pid":"848ba14b7f88378d1b4e76277d58c96ef65a313d","tid":149693,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"屌鳩M記加價<br />\n<br />\n仆街公司無鳩良！<br />\n<br />\n咬牙切齒<br />\n<br />\n下次去食要攞多兩包茄汁報仇<br />\n<br />\n但從來不追究自己既無能<br />\n<br />\n加個幾蚊比唔撚起"},{"pid":"fcff93fd357462e272d3bf9cd3d335e4a6095f31","tid":149693,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果行頭細 技術性高  三十 打後已冇可能轉行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n技術高有得撈都唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n但有時唔明d低技術既<br />\n<br />\n三十歲後你仲可以做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n求其請個後生平d人工取代你"},{"pid":"9b49f6c67732770a4b05240a17c49eeb12ee1d35","tid":149693,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"你溝唔到女<br />\n<br />\n所以女全部都係雞"},{"pid":"e2f10b32ab154a08351fe744d66b53d52d0ea8c0","tid":149693,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"當日成日比人屌鳩無用既八十後<br />\n<br />\n如大家所願<br />\n<br />\n都變成唔上唔水落無撚用既八十後廢中"},{"pid":"ea57406b6069ae21b6fda0e2d87f37ec07e5e337","tid":149693,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"廢中"},{"pid":"3f88cb9323ecec38e8258b9d74b1710f44f8aab3","tid":149693,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets